ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString:
If(
    With(
        {obj: ParseJSON(getEmail.result)},
        Text(obj.isApprover)
    ) = "True",
    true,
    false
)

If(
    IsMatch(
        With(
            {obj: ParseJSON(getEmail.result)},
            Text(obj.Title)
        ),
        "Head of",
        MatchOptions.Contains
    ) || IsMatch(
        With(
            {obj: ParseJSON(getEmail.result)},
            Text(obj.Title)
        ),
        "General Manager",
        MatchOptions.Complete
    ),
    true,
    false
)
If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))
